---
import Layout from "./_Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Rules | Open Sovereign Chess">
  <section class="page-header site-section">
    <div class="site-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Game introduction</p>
      <h1>Rules and learning path</h1>
      <p>
        This page can grow into a structured guide for Sovereign Chess. For now
        it points players to the official game material and gives the site a
        stable place for onboarding.
      </p>
      <div class="button-row">
        <a
          class="button primary"
          href="https://www.infinitepigames.com/sovereign-chess"
        >
          Official game site
        </a>
        <a class="button" href="/editor">Try the board</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="site-section">
    <div class="site-inner rules-grid">
      <article>
        <span>1</span>
        <h2>Start with normal chess instincts</h2>
        <p>
          Players still benefit from familiar chess concepts: king safety,
          development, material, and board control.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>2</span>
        <h2>Learn what makes ownership different</h2>
        <p>
          The variant introduces additional colors and control ideas, so new
          players need concise examples before they can evaluate positions.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>3</span>
        <h2>Practice with editable positions</h2>
        <p>
          The editor gives the site a practical way to teach rules through
          curated setups, puzzles, and examples later.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header .button-row {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .rules-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  article {
    min-height: 260px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--surface-strong);
  }

  article span {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 850;
  }

  article h2 {
    margin: 44px 0 10px;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  article p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.58;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .rules-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
